2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - CSO is a popular optimization algorithm in the field of artificial intelligence and has been used in various applications such as image processing, data mining, and machine learning. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - CSO has been used in machine learning applications such as feature selection and parameter optimization. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - CSO has been applied to control systems optimization problems. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - Although CSO is not specifically a data structure or algorithm, it is a popular optimization algorithm that can be used in conjunction with various data structures and algorithms.
